04:23.077 --> 04:24.344
Thank you, Mrs. lutz,

04:24.412 --> 04:26.013
and thank you, moms,
for your interest,

04:26.080 --> 04:28.282
but I just haven't met the one yet.

04:28.349 --> 04:30.384
Oh, for crying out loud, Liz.

04:30.451 --> 04:32.886
You see? That's what feminism does.

04:32.954 --> 04:36.290
It makes smart girls
with nice birthing shapes

04:36.357 --> 04:37.858
