04:42.330 --> 04:45.532
I'm waiting for
astronaut Mike Dexter.

04:45.600 --> 04:46.934
Oh, sweet lord in heaven.

04:47.001 --> 04:49.636
Who turns out to be the
secret king of Monaco.

04:49.704 --> 04:51.138
Liz, you're almost 40.

04:51.205 --> 04:53.907
You're not gonna find
some new kind of man.

04:53.975 --> 04:55.475
