05:46.227 --> 05:47.928
Go ahead. Feel 'em.
Feel the difference.

05:47.996 --> 05:49.896
Very different indeed.

05:49.964 --> 05:51.765
Like a cantaloupe

05:51.833 --> 05:55.802
and a ziploc bag of mushroom soup.

05:55.870 --> 05:57.471
