07:09.277 --> 07:11.712
Oh, hi. Are you going up?

07:11.779 --> 07:12.846
Down, actually.

07:12.914 --> 07:14.181
Ugh, I forgot my phone.

07:15.616 --> 07:18.285
Two women, Jack, at the same time.

07:18.352 --> 07:20.287
What are you, Italian?

07:20.354 --> 07:22.522
