have to choose.

07:47.615 --> 07:48.749
Hey.

07:48.816 --> 07:51.785
Um, why was I given this
to wear on the show?

07:51.853 --> 07:53.553
Well, I loved your idea

07:53.621 --> 07:55.288
that we both wear the same outfit.

07:55.356 --> 07:58.091
I just thought this one
might be more...Tv friendly.

07:58.159 --> 07:59.926
You mean instead of the rompers

07:59.994 --> 08:01.628
