08:01.696 --> 08:03.930
Mom, this isn't Florida.

08:03.998 --> 08:05.465
You're damn right it isn't.

08:05.533 --> 08:08.502
In Florida, everybody's
always asking me,

08:08.569 --> 08:10.637
"where did you get that?
You made it?

08:10.705 --> 08:13.573
Holy crap! Where do
I commission one?"

08:13.641 --> 08:16.943
Oh. This is about you
making money selling junk.

08:18.579 --> 08:20.080
Verna, this is my job,

08:20.148 --> 08:21.548
and I know you don't
understand that,

08:21.616 --> 08:23.316
