09:19.340 --> 09:21.441
I can't tell you what to do, Liz,

09:21.509 --> 09:24.678
but I know from
experience that that gu

09:24.745 --> 09:27.547
that perfect guy, is out there.

09:27.615 --> 09:29.883
'Cause I know I found mine.

09:29.951 --> 09:31.384
See, that's all I want.

09:31.452 --> 09:32.652
What you and dad have.

09:32.720 --> 09:34.821
Oh, I'm not talking
about your father.

09:34.889 --> 09:36.189
What?

09:38.426 --> 09:39.893
what do you mean you're
not talking about dad?

09:40.039 --> 09:41.205
You love dad. Of course I do,

09:41.273 --> 09:43.607
but Dick lemon isn't ed.

09:43.639 --> 09:44.739
Ed? Who's ed?

09:44.807 --> 09:47.709
Ed was my true love, sweetheart.

09:47.776 --> 09:50.778
He was my steady at montclair high.

09:50.846 --> 09:53.214
The night before he was
shipped off to Korea,

09:53.282 --> 09:56.117
