10:00.089 --> 10:01.155
Wait, what?

10:01.223 --> 10:03.458
Nothing, younger me. It's fine.

10:03.525 --> 10:05.226
He wanted to get married,

10:05.294 --> 10:06.794
but when he was invited to Houston

10:06.862 --> 10:08.396
for his astronaut training--

10:08.464 --> 10:09.864
