10:25.514 --> 10:28.283
So I settled for a wonderful man,

10:28.350 --> 10:30.585
and I have never regretted it.

10:30.653 --> 10:34.455
Not even when I watched ed
aldrin walk on the moon.

10:34.523 --> 10:38.293
Wait, your ed is buzz aldrin?

10:38.360 --> 10:40.161
Yeah, but I always called him ed,

10:40.229 --> 10:43.264
