10:50.906 --> 10:54.542
in the hbo original
movie <i>moon wives!</i>

10:55.878 --> 10:57.979
Where are you going, verna?

10:58.047 --> 10:59.547
Oh, I quit.

10:59.615 --> 11:01.582
I've been working my ass off

11:01.650 --> 11:03.685
