11:03.752 --> 11:05.553
but Jenna doesn't appreciate it.

11:05.621 --> 11:06.954
I see.

11:07.022 --> 11:09.023
Well, then good luck paying
for that other implant.

11:09.091 --> 11:10.992
It's not an implant, Jack.

11:11.060 --> 11:12.026
I mean, I got the meat.

11:12.094 --> 11:13.861
Of course. I apologize.

11:13.929 --> 11:16.364
Verna, you have a very
simple decision to make--

11:16.432 --> 11:18.032
