recognize you anyway.

11:34.116 --> 11:35.550
I'm sorry. What did you say?

11:35.617 --> 11:38.119
You are way beneath me, novella.

11:38.187 --> 11:40.555
I am a movie star,
a television actor,

11:40.622 --> 11:42.690
and a guinness book
of world record holder

11:42.758 --> 11:45.093
for most car accidents
in a single year.

11:45.160 --> 11:47.061
